@BookingService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5139
@Correlation = demo-correlation-001

### Liveness (process responds)
GET {{BookingService_HostAddress}}/health/live

### Readiness (degrades after consecutive failures or Health:SimulateCriticalDegradation)
GET {{BookingService_HostAddress}}/health/ready

### OpenAPI (Development)
GET {{BookingService_HostAddress}}/openapi/v1.json

###
### Prometheus scrape (booking.* metrics + ASP.NET Core)
GET {{BookingService_HostAddress}}/metrics

###
# Happy path: four steps, same process key
POST {{BookingService_HostAddress}}/api/processes/demo-1/events
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: {{Correlation}}

{
  "idempotencyKey": "step-1",
  "event": "ReserveRoom",
  "simulateFailure": false
}

###
POST {{BookingService_HostAddress}}/api/processes/demo-1/events
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: {{Correlation}}

{
  "idempotencyKey": "step-2",
  "event": "ConfirmDetails",
  "simulateFailure": false
}

###
POST {{BookingService_HostAddress}}/api/processes/demo-1/events
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: {{Correlation}}

{
  "idempotencyKey": "step-3",
  "event": "CapturePayment",
  "simulateFailure": false
}

###
POST {{BookingService_HostAddress}}/api/processes/demo-1/events
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: {{Correlation}}

{
  "idempotencyKey": "step-4",
  "event": "SendConfirmation",
  "simulateFailure": false
}

###
# Idempotent redelivery (duplicate: state unchanged, metrics redelivery++)
POST {{BookingService_HostAddress}}/api/processes/demo-1/events
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: redelivery-test

{
  "idempotencyKey": "step-1",
  "event": "ReserveRoom",
  "simulateFailure": false
}

###
# Simulated failure on next step -> compensation ReleaseRoom, back to Pending
POST {{BookingService_HostAddress}}/api/processes/demo-2/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idempotencyKey": "s1",
  "event": "ReserveRoom",
  "simulateFailure": false
}

###
POST {{BookingService_HostAddress}}/api/processes/demo-2/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idempotencyKey": "s2-fail",
  "event": "ConfirmDetails",
  "simulateFailure": true
}

###
GET {{BookingService_HostAddress}}/api/processes/demo-2

###
GET {{BookingService_HostAddress}}/api/processes/unknown-key
